usione|website=Museo Civico di Zoologia|language=it-IT|access-date=2019-04-28}}</ref>\n*[[Geological Museum, Rome|Geological Museum]], [[Rome]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.museogeologico.it/|title=Museo Geologico|website=www.museogeologico.it|access-date=2019-04-28}}</ref>\n* [[Museo Civico Rovereto]], [[Rovereto]]\n* [[Saint-Pierre Castle|Museo Regionale di Scienze Naturali]], [[Saint-Pierre, Aosta Valley|Saint-Pierre]]\n* Museo di Storia Naturale, [[Sulmona]]\n* Museo di Storia Naturale Bios Taras, [[Taranto]]\n* Museo Tridentino di Scienze Naturali, [[Trento]]\n* [[Civico Museo di Storia Naturale di Trieste]], [[Trieste]]\n* [[Turin Museum of Natural History]], [[Turin]]\n* [[Museo di Storia Naturale di Venezia]], [[Venice]]\n* Museo Civico di Storia Naturale, [[Verona]]\n\n===Latvia===\n*Natural History Museum of Latvia<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dabasmuzejs.gov.lv |title=Natural History Museum of Latvia |publisher=Dabasmuzejs.gov.lv |date= |accessdate=April 19, 2012}}</ref>\n\n===Liechtenstein===\n*[[Liechtenstein National Museum]], [[Vaduz]]\n\n===Lithuania===\n*[[Palanga Amber Museum]], [[Palanga]]\n*[[Tadas Ivanauskas Zoological Museum]], [[Kaunas]]\n\n===Luxembourg===\n*[[National Museum of Natural History Luxembourg]], [[Luxembourg City]]\n\n===Macedonia===\n*[[Macedonian Museum of Natural History]], [[Skopje]]\n\n===Malta===\n*[[National Museum of Natural History, Malta|National Museum of Natural History]], [[Mdina]]\n\n===Moldova===\n*[[National Museum of Ethnography and Natural History]], [[Chi\u0219in\u0103u]]\n\n===Monaco===\n*[[Oceanographic Museum]], [[Monaco-Ville]]\n\n===Montenegro===\n*Natural History Museum of Montenegro, [[Podgorica]]\n\n===The Netherlands===\n* [[Naturalis]] (or National Museum of Natural History), [[Leiden]]\n*[[Maastricht Natural History Museum|Natuurhistorisch Museum Maastricht]], [[Maastricht]]\n*[[Natuurhistorisch Museum Rotterdam]], [[Rotterdam]]\n*[[Oertijdmuseum]], [[Boxtel]]\n*[[Teylers Museum]], [[Haarlem]]\n*[