os]]\n*Mus\u00e9e min\u00e8ralogique et minier de Thetford Mines, [[Thetford Mines]]\n*[[Redpath Museum]], [[Montreal]]\n\n====Saskatchewan====\n* Abernethy Nature-Heritage Museum, [[Abernethy, Saskatchewan|Abernethy]]\n*[[Ancient Echoes Interpretive Centre|Ancient Echoes Interpretive Center]],<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ancientechoes.ca/|title=Home|website=www.ancientechoes.ca|access-date=January 28, 2019}}</ref> [[Herschel, Saskatchewan|Herschel]]\n*Museum of Natural Sciences, [[University of Saskatchewan]], [[Saskatoon]]\n*[[Royal Saskatchewan Museum]], [[Regina, Saskatchewan|Regina]]\n*T.rex Discover Centre, [[Eastend, Saskatchewan|Eastend]]\n\n====Yukon====\n*Kluane Museum of Natural History, [[Burwash Landing, Yukon|Burwash Landing]]\n*Yukon Beringia Interpretive Centre, [[Whitehorse, Yukon|Whitehorse]]\n\n===Mexico===\n* Caracol, Museo de Ciencias de Ensenada, [[Ensenada, Baja California|Ensenada]]\n* Museo de Geolog\u00eda UNAM, [[Mexico City]]\n* Museo de Historia Natural de la Ciudad de M\u00e9xico, [[Mexico City]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://travel.nytimes.com/travel/guides/north-america/mexico/mexico-city/attraction-detail.html?vid=1154654609195 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120715155119/http://travel.nytimes.com/travel/guides/north-america/mexico/mexico-city/attraction-detail.html?vid=1154654609195 |url-status=dead |archive-date=July 15, 2012 |title=NY Times description |publisher=Travel.nytimes.com |date= |accessdate=April 19, 2012 }}</ref>\n* Museo de las Aves de M\u00e9xico, [[Coahuila]]\n*Museo de Paleontolog\u00eda de Delicias, [[Chihuahua, Chihuahua|Chihuahua]]\n* Museo de Paleontolog\u00eda de Guadalajara, [[Guadalajara, Jalisco|Guadalajara]]\n*Museo de Paleontolog\u00eda- UNAM, [[Mexico City]]\n* Museo del Desierto, [[Coahuila]]\n* [[Museo Nacional de Antropologia]], [[Mexico City]]\n* Tamux \u2013 Museo de Historia Natural de Tamaulipas, [[Tamaulipas]]\n* [[Paleontological Museum in Tocuila|Museo Paleontol\u00f3gico en Tocuila]], [[Te